      <ul>
        <li>Analogue electronics design</li>
        <li>Protoboarding</li>
        <li>PCB Design</li>
        <li>Surface mount soldering</li>
        <li>ESP32 microcontroller programming</li>
        <li>Real time operating systems</li>
        <li>Pose estimation</li>
        <li>Control system design</li>
      </ul>
